README for trinity-extra-theme


NOTES

  vim
  ---
  
  :colorscheme Trinity
  
  
  hexchat
  -------
  
  cp /usr/share/trinity/hexchat ~/.config/hexchat/colors.conf
  
  
  Xresources
  ----------
  
  Put the following line in ~/.Xresources:
  #include "/usr/share/trinity/Xresources"
  
  And the following line in ~/.xinitrc for persistent setting:
  [[ -f ~/.Xresources ]] && xrdb -merge ~/.Xresources


End of file.
